Package: adRutils
Type: Package
Version: 0.2.0
Title: Utility Functions for Data Processing in R
Authors@R: c(person("Ana", "Boeriu", email = "ana.boeriu@ucsf.edu",role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: A collection of utility functions for data cleaning, transformation, file operations. Provides tools 
    for reading pattern-matched CSV files, handling missing values, standardizing data formats, 
     caching mechanisms for API calls, and tracking functions to prevent duplicate operations.
    prevent duplicate operations and parameter validation
